\end{equation}

\end_inset

Az energia szórása
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{eqnarray}
\left\langle E^{2}\right\rangle -\left\langle E\right\rangle ^{2} & = & \varepsilon^{2}N(N-1)\tanh^{2}\beta\varepsilon+N\varepsilon^{2}-N^{2}\varepsilon^{2}\tanh^{2}\beta\varepsilon\\
